    public class EndView

    EndView

    This End class is refactored from original End class, has 4 status in total. It is extended from View class:
    Refactor:
    1. This class is purely used for demonstration;
    2. Moved the methods related to End status to EndModel and EndController;

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.3
    Author:
    Kejia Wu, scykw1@nottingham.ac.uk
    See Also:
    View, EndModel, EndController
